==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reseda
<hw>Re*se"da</hw> <pr>(r?-s?"d?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. , a kind
of plant.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of plants,
the type of which is mignonette.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A grayish green color, like that of the flowers of
mignonette.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reseek</ent>⟦br⟧
